HEADWORD: Covellite
<hw>Co*vel"lite</hw>  }</mhw> <pr>(-l?t)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[After <ets>Covelli</ets>, the discoverer.]</ety> <fld>(Min.)</fld> <def>A native sulphide of copper, occurring in masses of a dark blue color; -- hence called <altname>indigo copper</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
